## Release v9.2.0

### Balancing

- Player gradually gets higher prices for their goods every levels
- Increased player ship storage
- Increased maximum number of purchasable weapon damage upgrades

### Bugs

- Moved version number on the title screen 1 pixel down
- Fixed bug where shields did not remove credits from your account
- Fixed price for damage upgrades
- Fixed a bug where the player could not purchase any more damage upgrades
- Fixed wront calculation of weapon damage increase on buying and loading the game
- Fixed a bug where picking up a shield pick-up would restore the shield of a destroyed drone
- Skipping trade after beating the last level

## Files included

- `void-merchants.p8` — PICO-8 standard cart in clear text format
- `void-merchants.p8.png` — PICO-8 cart image
- `void-merchants_linux.zip` — Linux binaries
- `void-merchants_windows.zip` — Windows binaries
- `void-merchants_raspi.zip` — Raspberry Pi binaries
- `void-merchants_osx.zip` — macOS binaries
- `manual.txt` — Manual for this release
- `LICENSE.txt` — Licensing information